-of-the-earth-dates-buy-tickets-3613347">在此处</a>查看完整详细信息，并<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fglass-animals-tickets%2Fartist%2F1916866" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>查找任何剩余的门票。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="433" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="2" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-big-moon-here-is-everything-review-3328102"><b>《The Big Moon》——《Here Is Everything》评论：他们迄今为止最深刻、最感人的专辑</b></a></li></ul><p>该乐队上一次发行专辑是在 2022 年，《Here Is Everything》是他们的第三张 LP，收录了单曲《Wide Eyes》、《Trouble》和《This Love》。</p><p> <i>NME</i><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-big-moon-here-is-everything-review-3328102">在对该专辑的四星评论中</a>写道：“可能会有像《Suckerpunch》中详述的那样糟糕的日子，但总有希望。这些曲目不仅对杰克逊和她的故事具有个人意义，而且仍然被普遍感受到。从他们的笔到他们的声音，《Here Is Everything》充满情感且光彩夺目；一个在这个忙碌的世界中提供呼吸空间的人。”</p><p> Big Moon 在整个夏天进行了多场演出，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/patti-smith-corinne-bailey-rae-the-amazons-and-more-lead-somerset-house-summer-series-2024-line-up-3602215">7 月份的萨默塞特宫夏季系列赛</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallagher-confirms-support-acts-for-huge-uk-summer-2024-shows-3598634">卡迪夫城堡诺尔·加拉格尔 (Noel Gallagher) 的《高飞鸟》 (High Flying Birds) 的开场表演</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-charlatans-mary-wallopers-futureheads-and-more-join-massive-line-up-for-the-libertines-brighton-beach-gig-3584943">布莱顿海滩 (Brighton Beach) 的浪子乐队 (The Libertines) 演出</a>以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallagher-confirms-support-acts-for-huge-uk-summer-2024-shows-3598634">大胡子理论节 (Bearded Theory Festival)</a>的一部分五月<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallagher-confirms-support-acts-for-huge-uk-summer-2024-shows-3598634">在德比郡</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-big-moons-juliette-jackson-marries-partner-at-green-man-festival-10-years-after-they-met-on-the-same-site-3784676">《Big Moon》的朱丽叶·杰克逊 (Juliette Jackson) 在绿人节 (Green Man Festival) 与伴侣结婚——他们在同一个网站相识 10 年后，这篇</a>文章首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
